<div class="toggle-content">
  <h3 id="go-slices-are-divided-into-shallow-copy-and-deep-copy">Go slices are divided into shallow copy and deep copy</h3>
<h4 id="shallow-copy">Shallow Copy</h4>
<p>A Go slice consists of length, capacity, and an underlying array. A shallow copy only duplicates the slice header (slice pointer, length, and capacity).
Since the underlying array of slices is shared, modifying slice elements will affect other slices.</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
